		<title>Review: HP Mini 1000 Netbook Earns Notebooks.com Editor&#8217;s Choice Award</title>
		<link>http://www.notebooks.com/2008/12/10/review-hp-mini-1000-netbook-earns-notebookscom-editors-choice-award/</link>
		<comments>http://www.notebooks.com/2008/12/10/review-hp-mini-1000-netbook-earns-notebookscom-editors-choice-award/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 10 Dec 2008 11:09:53 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Xavier</dc:creator>
		
